PRICE v. WILKES et al. (Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. February 3, 1923.) No. 3908. J. H. Mize, of Gulfport, Miss., j.or plaintiff in error. B„ E. Eaton and W. A. White, both of Gulfport, *1022Miss., for defendants in error.

Before WALKER, BRYAN, and KING, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The record in this case shows no reversible error. The Judgment is affirmed.
